    //   headless           → API providers only (OpenAI//Anthropic/etc) → Local
    //   smoke-test profile → Codex CLI →  CLI flash-lite → Claude CLI → Local
    //   full profile       → Codex CLI →  CLI fallthrough → OpenAI → Local →
